articles.title: Squid Game fever is real, here's how Singaporeans are joining the game - AsiaOne
articles.description: Everyone loves Squid Game, and you can't escape its influence on the Internet. Since its release on Sept 17, original series Squid Game has become the number one trending show on Netflix in Singapore, and the first Korean show to rank #1 on the same platform …
